summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Engineering authorizing the execution and acceptance of Easement Agreement No. 36691 from the State of Washington, Department of Natural Resources for a storm drain outfall in a portion of the Public Place located in Elliott Bay of Puget Sound at the foot of Fairmount Avenue S.W. in conjunction with Forward Thrust Sewer Improvement Project No. 9, West Seattle-Alki, Contract 4.
